{
  "stem": "5371.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there's an oven there, and I should-- there's like, gratings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I should break the gratings with a hammer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they gave me new gratings, and I should put in new gratings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But while I'm doing with this, I should put in potatoes on the bottom of the pail, and cover it with, with the rag, and the the clay-- whatever's left of the clay on top, and the tools, and walk out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The problem was that the SS in there were walking around everywhere, you know, And in the doorway, as you walked out, the SS men stood also.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I luckily passed him by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he didn't look inside the pail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they made me do a lot of those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One time, a truck that brought in the bread to camp had a, a big [? tarpark, ?] you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Covered with a [? tarpark. ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they told me I should jump up on the truck, and stay there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And take a couple loaves of bread, and then jump out and run back to the building where, where I'm working.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they made me-- they used to do-- they, they used to-- they allowed-- they allowed them to have an oven made out of a-- like a primitive oven, out, out of a barrel.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what they did is, they put some grating inside, and they used to cook inside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they made me stay-- but they weren't allowed to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they told me to stay outside and watch, like a watchman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See if anyone coming, either SS or anybody from the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But if they saw you standing there doing nothing, you were, you were, you were punished too.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
